channel.title: Netgear Router problems :(
channel.description:
Ok, so i got a router .. and now i cant portfoward . .cause i dont know the username and password to get on the website to portforward (192.168.1.1)
Im the only person in my house that uses this router, and i/nobody has set a user or password for it (exept for our connections) I have tried my connection password and everything =/
If anyone can help can you please tell me how to get my username and password for my router - Netgear router
Thanks
